  - Loader fills from effective header to effective footer (respecting notches, home indicator).
  - Test on iOS PWA installed (Add to Home Screen) or simulator with safe area.
  - Preserve S54 viewport invariants (100dvh where applicable).

###############################################################################
# DELIVERABLES
###############################################################################
out: [Loader component: safe area insets applied]
done:
